> > > The logic is changed to get the default value which is closest to the
> > > calculated value [1]
> > > 
> > > Calculated value 360Mbps : Default 350Mbps  Range [320.625 -380.625 mpbs]
> > > 
> > > [1] specs r19uh0105ej0200-r-car-3rd-generation.pdf [Table 25.9]
